Package: PhenoPacketR
Type: Package
Title: Package to work with PhenoPackets (v2.0) in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Adam", "Klocperk",
      email = "adamklocperk@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A unified toolkit for programmatically creating, annotating, and sanitizing GA4GH-compliant 
      phenopacket JSONs from Excel templates, including functions to generate new packets, append HPO-based 
      phenotypes, add genomic interpretations, and update obsolete ontology terms.
